<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Maze Bots</title>
<style>
  body { 
    background: #121212; 
    color: #eee; 
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
    display: flex; 
    flex-direction: column; 
    align-items: center; 
    justify-content: center; 
    height: 100vh; 
